{"tid":2065572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無手足/議員幫手處理太古廣場出面既花同禮物？","createTime":"2020-06-15T15:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T17:11:51.000Z","uid":3354,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"19bfd81b8190132ab3c51dc3cbf333c7c5a5b438","tid":2065572,"uid":3354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"記得上年616遊行之後 因為落雨有啲花開始爛<br />\n然後有手足加埋花藝師自發整理好啲花<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/cat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/cat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一年過去 情況唔同左 都未知啲狗今晚會唔會就拆左個壇<br />\n或者會唔會有藍絲聽朝一早去摧毀啲花同禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知今日大家獻既花或者禮物會唔會有議員嗰啲幫手轉達俾梁先生既屋企人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者有無咩方法處理啲花唔好就咁俾人掉左佢咁浪費？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315f15dea8ca2edff433d28fb4241bc4b115b95b","tid":2065572,"uid":3354,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T15:59:20.000Z","msg":"自推一下<br />\n喺上年個post到搵到啲各個手足同花藝師一齊合作之後既對比圖<br />\n今年情況唔同 未必可以當文宣 連儂牆咁擺<br />\n唔知有咩可以做到 大家集思廣益下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LTEeAAM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLTEeAAM.png&h=0916d181&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oiHWOVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoiHWOVN.png&h=4e08ea08&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gp0pXO8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGp0pXO8.png&h=a168bb26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2a4a2ace41446d5e16b2ac439c485d62c390441","tid":2065572,"uid":3354,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"唔想啲花同禮物拎黎影完相畫面好靚之後就掉左佢<br />\n有啲黃店特登免費送花俾大家悼念 <br />\n都唔好就咁浪費左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ef57057ca5d60817d547dbcdd3ca15f11e5718","tid":2065572,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:02:06.000Z","msg":"應該半夜就搵食環吊雞車一野夾走晒"},{"pid":"d04c73ede98f0957b5bf8adcf75c2e125d823e71","tid":2065572,"uid":3354,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:03:12.000Z","msg":"今日見到大家擺低既花 畫作 禮物 文宣都好靚<br />\n有啲相信都幾有紀念價值 <br />\n唔知有無議員幫手跟進？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d1df67ddbc8728cf6134c9317c73b72611b7eb","tid":2065572,"uid":3354,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"63ef57057ca5d60817d547dbcdd3ca15f11e5718","tid":2065572,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:02:06.000Z","msg":"應該半夜就搵食環吊雞車一野夾走晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣好浪費 好多鮮花都好靚 甚至開都未開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0b8ba9ebea047a1a071304ed934e17bf2981ee","tid":2065572,"uid":3354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:05:38.000Z","msg":"推下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想見到啲狗又好似平時太子站咁亂咁拆亂咁掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b26a45f5b2c6d85b103e0355512ea2b8af36373","tid":2065572,"uid":3354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:07:41.000Z","msg":"集思廣益下 如果垃圾政府今晚唔處理既話<br />\n聽日有無可能等手足返工食飯放工一齊執下整理下<br />\n再由議員代送咁？"},{"pid":"1fbcd0e69b58d34a46e2f21755efce754e19c6e7","tid":2065572,"uid":3354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:08:46.000Z","msg":"一推再推 大家有無咩諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7814f9ea32800c0a098de6a51cb76afafbe4ed7f","tid":2065572,"uid":74858,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:09:41.000Z","msg":"d 花都轉交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />梁先生屋企人應該唔會想收萬幾支花掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1203db2dbd9c98fdc288fb878d7c27cf61490e4a","tid":2065572,"uid":3354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7814f9ea32800c0a098de6a51cb76afafbe4ed7f","tid":2065572,"uid":74858,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:09:41.000Z","msg":"d 花都轉交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />梁先生屋企人應該唔會想收萬幾支花掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:11:14.000Z","msg":"主要係禮物或者卡片可以轉交<br />\n但係鮮花就咁掉晒佢好似都好浪費 <br />\n所以想知會唔會有方法可以處理得好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a356acdb453cd2aad9ddd3be6579d3c2851def46","tid":2065572,"uid":3354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:13:03.000Z","msg":"再推下先 好似上面巴打咁講<br />\n花無可能送俾烈士屋企人<br />\n但就咁掉左又好浪費 有無花藝巴絲有建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9835c7776d269ac27c17876ccdf9cb119068e231","tid":2065572,"uid":3354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:15:04.000Z","msg":"推下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac